1. This function takes in an argument, args.
2. It then creates a new keyword called port and assigns it the value of the environment variable PORT, or 9837.
3. It then creates a new keyword called thread and assigns it the value of 8.
4. It then creates a new keyword called max-body and assigns it the value of 8388608.
5. It then runs the server with the arguments app, port, thread, and max-body
